<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4296379>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 5–7. Male genitalia of Rhyacophila spp. 5, R. fasciata delici Kučinić & Valladolid ssp. nov. 6, R. fasciata viteceki Valladolid & Kučinić ssp. nov. 7, R. f. fasciata Hagen, 1859. 5a–7a, 2nd segment of left inferior appendage, left lateral; 5b–7b, apicodorsal lobe and preanal appendages, dorsal; 5c–7c, parameres and aedeagus (phallicata), ventral; 5d–7d, left paramere, left lateral; 5e–7e, aedeagus (phallicata) and ventral lobe, left lateral. Scale bars: a–c = 0.5 mm, d–e = 250 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4296379/files/figure.png" .

