<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4296374>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1, 2. Male and female genitalia of Rhyacophila fasciata delici Kučinić & Valladolid ssp. nov. 1, male: 1A, 2nd segment of left inferior appendage, left lateral; 1BV–1BL, parameres: 1BV, parameres (p) and ventral lobe of aedeagus (phallicata) (vl), ventral; 1BL, left paramere, left lateral. 1CL–1CD, aedeagus (phallicata) and lateroventral lobes: 1CL, aedeagus and ventral lobe, lateral; 1CD, aedeagus and lateroventral lobes (lvl), dorsal. 1DD, apicodorsal lobe of segment IX (al) and preanal appendages (pa); 1DV, segment X, ventral, ab = apical band, as = anal sclerites, va = non-sclerotized ventral area. 2, female segments VIII–XI: 2L, left lateral; 2D, dorsal; 2V, ventral. Scale bars: unlabelled = 1 mm; circle = 0.5 mm; asterisk = 250 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4296374/files/figure.png" .

